            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>New Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Auto update with Sparkle framework. Auto updated works only when run the main application and not from the quicklook extension.</li>
                    <li>In the Preferences window, new button to show UTI instead of the extensions.</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Bugfix</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Regression fix about data limit.</li>
                    <li>Better layout for the list of the supported languages.</li>
                </ul>
