            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>New Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Toolbar and touchbar for access to the inquiry and themes window.</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Bugfix</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Cosmetic fix for Big Sur.</li>
                    <li>The html output mode fail on Big Sur. It would appear that there is a bug preventing the recognition of the extension entitlements which causes webkit to fail to run. The use of the deprecated WebView temporarily bypasses the problem.</li>
                    <li>Closing the preferences window with unsaved settings show a confirmation popup</li>
                </ul>
            ]]>
            </description>
